Description: The Vertical shoulder bag by Moncler is made of soft leather with thermoformed boudin quilting, reminiscent of the iconic down jackets. The Off-White Day Off mini tote bag is made of nylon with contrasting logo lettering and handles in woven tape with metal rivets.
